	• Use the 'tube' to go downstairs to collect the keys.
	• Use the 'ladder' to go back upstairs after you have both keys.
	• The 'door' can only be opened after you have collected both keys.
	• You can move using 'left', 'right', 'up', or 'down'.

At each step, you will receive a description of the maze and must decide which direction to move.

You have moved to down cell.
